{"tid":1421812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭一定要對凖政府！","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:04:05.000Z","uid":73956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b00ba32f194737c153d7392b29b109b7439b8bf","tid":1421812,"uid":73956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">明白</span>各位用<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔同方法努力為香港</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">知道阻塞交通同罷工</span>可以使人工收入減少，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府稅收減少</span>，<br />\n為社會帶來不便，<br />\n對政府施壓，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">逼政府跟民意，五大訴求</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不過有人係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">手停口停</span>，<br />\n阻塞交通同罷工，可能<span style=\"font-size: large;\">傷及無辜</span>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">輸中間派同温和派民意</span>。<br />\n<br />\n市民要表達意見，可以去<span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府地方</span>，<br />\n包括禮賓府、立法局、警署及不同政府部門，<br />\n或尋找<span style=\"font-size: large;\">立法會議員</span>表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不割蓆</span>，不過希望爭取<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最大民意</span>、<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最大力量</span>。"},{"pid":"459be369f0474c59275f351f9997b929c4770483","tid":1421812,"uid":253833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"和理非新回合<br />\n［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}